{"translation-revision-date":"2025-02-04T15:33:29+00:00","generator":"WP-CLI\/2.12.0","source":"admin-core\/assets\/build\/onboarding-app.js","domain":"messages","locale_data":{"messages":{"":{"domain":"messages","lang":"en","plural-forms":"nplurals=2; plural=(n != 1);"},"Spectra":["Spektren"],"Elementor":["Elementor"],"Bricks":["Ziegel"],"Other":["Andere"],"Email address":["E-Mail-Adresse"],"Reset":["Zur\u00fccksetzen"],"Processing":["Verarbeitung"],"Access all of our pro templates when you upgrade your plan to CartFlows Pro today.":["Greifen Sie auf alle unsere Pro-Vorlagen zu, wenn Sie Ihr Abonnement noch heute auf CartFlows Pro upgraden."],"Get CartFlows Pro":["Holen Sie sich CartFlows Pro"],"Back":["Zur\u00fcck"],"Importing..":["Importieren.."],"Active":["Aktiv"],"Let's Start":["Lass uns anfangen"],"Welcome to CartFlows":["Willkommen bei CartFlows"],"You're only minutes away from having a more profitable WooCommerce store! This short setup wizard will help you get started with CartFlows.":["Sie sind nur wenige Minuten davon entfernt, einen profitableren WooCommerce-Shop zu haben! Dieser kurze Einrichtungsassistent hilft Ihnen, mit CartFlows zu beginnen."],"Save & Continue":["Speichern & Fortfahren"],"Saving":["Speichern"],"Hi there! Tell us which page builder you use.":["Hallo! Sag uns, welchen Page Builder du benutzt."],"Install & Activate":["Installieren & Aktivieren"],"Installing Required Plugins":["Installation erforderlicher Plugins"],"Since CartFlows uses WooCommerce, we'll set it up for you along with Cart Abandonment and Stripe Payments so you can recover abandoned orders and easily accept payments.":["Da CartFlows WooCommerce verwendet, richten wir es f\u00fcr Sie zusammen mit Warenkorbabbruch und Stripe-Zahlungen ein, damit Sie verlassene Bestellungen zur\u00fcckgewinnen und Zahlungen einfach akzeptieren k\u00f6nnen."],"Continuing\u2026":["Fortsetzung\u2026"],"Continue":["Fortfahren"],"First Name":["Vorname"],"Please enter your name":["Bitte geben Sie Ihren Namen ein"],"Enter Your Email":["Geben Sie Ihre E-Mail ein"],"Please Enter Name":["Bitte Namen eingeben"],"Entered email address is not a valid email":["Die eingegebene E-Mail-Adresse ist keine g\u00fcltige E-Mail"],"Please Enter Email ID":["Bitte E-Mail-ID eingeben"],"Skip":["\u00dcberspringen"],"Select Color":["Farbe ausw\u00e4hlen"],"Recommended":["Empfohlen"],"Upload a Logo":["Laden Sie ein Logo hoch"],"Change a Logo":["Ein Logo \u00e4ndern"],"Remove logo":["Logo entfernen"],"Suggested Dimensions: 180x60 pixels":["Vorgeschlagene Abmessungen: 180x60 Pixel"],"Oops!!! No templates found":["Hoppla!!! Keine Vorlagen gefunden"],"Seems like no templates are available for chosen page editor. Don't worry, you can always import the store checkout template from the CartFlows setting menu.":["Es scheint, dass keine Vorlagen f\u00fcr den ausgew\u00e4hlten Seiteneditor verf\u00fcgbar sind. Keine Sorge, Sie k\u00f6nnen die Store-Checkout-Vorlage jederzeit aus dem CartFlows-Einstellungsmen\u00fc importieren."],"Skip to Next":["Zum N\u00e4chsten springen"],"Now let's setup your new store checkout.":["Richten wir jetzt die Kasse Ihres neuen Gesch\u00e4fts ein."],"Choose one of the store checkout designs below. After setup you can change the text and color or even choose an entirely new store checkout design.":["W\u00e4hlen Sie eines der unten stehenden Kassen-Designs aus. Nach der Einrichtung k\u00f6nnen Sie den Text und die Farbe \u00e4ndern oder sogar ein v\u00f6llig neues Kassen-Design w\u00e4hlen."],"Import & Continue":["Importieren & Fortfahren"],"Processing..":["Verarbeitung.."],"Importing Failed..":["Importieren fehlgeschlagen.."],"Change Primary Color":["Prim\u00e4rfarbe \u00e4ndern"],"Learn more about usage tracking":["Erfahren Sie mehr \u00fcber die Nutzungsverfolgung"],"Documentation":[""],"Something went wrong":[""],"An unexpected error occurred while loading this section. Refreshing the page should fix the issue.":[""],"Go Back":[""],"Refresh Page":[""],"Block Builder":[""],"Beaver Builder":[""],"Exit Guided Setup":[""],"Awesome \ud83d\udc4d":[""],"Set up a high-converting checkout page in minutes":[""],"Recover abandoned orders with built-in cart abandonment":[""],"Accept payments easily with Stripe integration":[""],"Works seamlessly with your existing page builder":[""],"Boost revenue with upsells, downsells, and order bumps":[""],"CartFlows \u2014 Welcome Walkthrough":[""],"Get Started with Onboarding":[""],"CartFlows works with all page builders, so don't worry if your page builder is not in the list.":[""],"Great job! Now let's install some required plugins.":[""],"Not Installed":[""],"Previous templates":[""],"Next templates":[""],"One last step.":[""],"Let's setup email reports on how your store is doing.":[""],"Let CartFlows take the guesswork out of your checkout results. Each week your store will send you an email report with key metrics and insights. You also will receive emails from us to help your store sell more.":[""],"Help improve CartFlows by sharing non-sensitive usage data.":[""],"We don't collect any personal information\u2014just basic details like your PHP version, admin language, and which features you use.":[""],"Learn more":[""],"about what we collect and why.":[""],"High-converting checkout pages":[""],"Your store now has optimized checkout pages ready to convert visitors into customers.":[""],"Cart abandonment recovery":[""],"Automatically recover lost sales with built-in cart abandonment emails.":[""],"Revenue-boosting funnels":[""],"Upsells, downsells, and order bumps are ready to maximize your average order value.":[""],"Congratulations, You Did it! \ud83c\udf89":[""],"CartFlows is set up on your website! You're now ready to build high-converting sales funnels.":[""],"Here's What You've Unlocked:":[""],"Redirecting\u2026":[""],"Go To Dashboard":[""]}}}